<br>
Used to be: Base Regen + Troll/Iksar regen bonus + 12 hp/tick  (if you had both general regen and arch regen maxed)<br>
<br>
Now: Base Regen + Troll/Iksar regen bonus + 6hp/tick (again, if you have both)<br>
<br>
<br>
So they're no worse off than anyone else with the skills, and given that there is no racial penalty to AA XP gaining, I don't have any problem with everyone being the same. Honestly, they should set the arch skill regen to 2pts per level, since it costs so much more (so that everyone would be at +9hp/tick if they had both), but that's just me.<br>
<br>
There was/is a HUGE thread on the monk boards about this. Absor actually posted, and said that it was not a bug that they were getting 2x the regen from the same point expenditure, the live team &quot;basically came to the conclusion that there really isn?t any reason for two races to get more from the same ability than all the other races.&quot;<br>
<br>
I can't say as I disagree with that logic.....<br>
